---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Automatic Nation — Automation &amp; Integrations Agency</title>
  <meta name="description" content="We build custom integrations and automated workflows across Airtable, n8n, and 9,000+ apps. 50+ workflows shipped. Book a discovery call." />

  <!-- Fonts: hero set + JetBrains Mono for section eyebrows -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;700&family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <!-- Tailwind CDN — only powers the imported sections below the hero -->
  <!-- is:inline keeps Astro from hoisting/bundling these CDN tags -->
  <script is:inline src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script is:inline>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            ink:    '#2c2c2c',
            paper:  '#ffffff',
            mute:   '#525252',
            dim:    '#A3A3A3',
            line:   '#E5E5E5',
            lineDk: '#484848',
            accent: '#f6da74',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            sans: ["'Space Grotesk'", "'Montserrat'", 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],
            mono: ['"JetBrains Mono"', 'ui-monospace', 'monospace'],
          },
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <style is:global>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      background: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* ── Navbar ── */
    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 120px;
      height: 88px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #2c2c2c;
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .logo svg { flex-shrink: 0; }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      flex: 1;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 40px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #000;
      text-transform: capitalize;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { opacity: 0.6; }

    .btn-cta {
      background: #f6da74;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 70px;
      padding: 16px 24px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #000;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-transform: capitalize;
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-cta:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 72px;
      padding: 0 121px;
      height: calc(100vh - 88px);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .hero-left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      max-width: 561px;
    }

    .headline {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 72px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -4px;
      color: #000;
      text-transform: capitalize;
    }
    .headline strong { font-weight: 700; }

    .hero-sub {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 36px;
      color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      max-width: 508px;
    }

    .hero-sub2 {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 32px;
      color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      max-width: 508px;
    }

    .email-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .email-input {
      background: #fafafa;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      border-radius: 37px;
      padding: 20px 18px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #aaa;
      width: 339px;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .email-input:focus { border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.5); color: #000; }

    .btn-submit {
      background: #f6da74;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 70px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      width: 146px;
      height: 64px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #000;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-transform: capitalize;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-submit:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

    /* ── Hero right: dot card ── */
    .hero-right { flex-shrink: 0; }

    .dot-card {
      width: 608px;
      height: 608px;
      background: #2c2c2c;
      border-radius: 32px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    #dotCanvas {
      display: block;
      width: 608px;
      height: 608px;
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0;
    }

    .float-card {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 76px;
      height: 76px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      will-change: transform;
    }
    .float-card img { width: 48px; height: 48px; object-fit: contain; pointer-events: none; user-select: none; -webkit-user-drag: none; }
    .float-card { user-select: none; }

    .float-card--count {
      background: #f6da74;
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #2c2c2c;
    }

    .float-card--profile { padding: 0; overflow: hidden; }
    .float-card--profile img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

    /* ── Section helpers (used by Tailwind sections below) ── */
    .tracking-tight2 { letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
    .tracking-tight3 { letter-spacing: -0.035em; }
    .leading-95      { line-height: 0.95; }

    .eyebrow {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .link-u { position: relative; }
    .link-u::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: -2px; height: 1px;
      background: currentColor; transform: scaleX(0); transform-origin: left;
      transition: transform .25s ease;
    }
    .link-u:hover::after { transform: scaleX(1); }

    .cta { transition: transform .15s ease, background-color .15s ease; }
    .cta:hover { transform: scale(1.02); }

    /* dotted bg for dark sections — matches hero canvas (2 px radius, 35 px gap, 15% opacity) */
    .dot-grid {
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 2px, transparent 2px);
      background-size: 35px 35px;
    }

    /* reveal-on-scroll */
    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); transition: opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease; }
    .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    /* horizontal scroll snap (mobile use-cases row) */
    .h-snap { scroll-snap-type: x mandatory; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; }
    .h-snap > * { scroll-snap-align: start; }

    .no-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
    .no-scrollbar { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }

    .h2-display { font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px); }
    .h2-xl      { font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  NAVBAR                                    -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<nav class="navbar">
  <a href="#" class="logo">
    <svg width="32" height="31" viewBox="0 0 32 31" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M11.6217 0C11.7142 0.000353627 11.7891 0.0752685 11.7895 0.167763V21.8947H13.4737V12.125L20.2105 0H21.8947V21.8947H23.5789V12.125L30.3158 0H32V15.1579H30.3158L21.8947 30.3158H20.2105V15.1579L11.7895 30.3158H10.1053V15.8076C10.105 15.6342 9.87405 15.5741 9.78947 15.7253L1.73191 30.2286C1.70227 30.282 1.64653 30.3156 1.58553 30.3158H0.167763C0.0752688 30.3154 0.000354051 30.2405 0 30.148V15.3257C0.000354057 15.2332 0.0752688 15.1582 0.167763 15.1579H1.58553C1.64653 15.1577 1.70227 15.1241 1.73191 15.0707L10.0576 0.087171C10.0872 0.0338245 10.1429 0.00014998 10.2039 0H11.6217Z" fill="#2C2C2C"/>
    </svg>
    Automatic Nation
  </a>
  <nav class="nav-links">
    <a href="#templates">Use cases</a>
    <a href="#process">Process</a>
    <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
  </nav>
  <a href="#book" class="btn-cta">Book a call</a>
</nav>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  HERO                                      -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <h1 class="headline">
      Save your team<br>
      <strong>22 hours</strong> a week<br>
      of manual work.
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      We build custom integrations and automated workflows across 900+ popular platforms.
    </p>
    <p class="hero-sub2">
      First system live in under 4 weeks, fixed scope, fixed price.
    </p>
    <div class="email-row">
      <input class="email-input" type="email" placeholder="Enter your Email" />
      <button class="btn-submit">Lets Talk</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="dot-card">
      <canvas id="dotCanvas" width="608" height="608"></canvas>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  WHO IT'S FOR                              -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="who-its-for" class="bg-paper border-t border-line">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow text-mute mb-4">Who this is for</p>
      <h2 class="h2-display font-bold tracking-tight3 leading-95">This pays off fastest if you're…</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 divide-y sm:divide-y-0 sm:divide-x divide-line border border-line reveal">
      <div class="p-8 lg:p-10">
        <p class="eyebrow text-mute mb-4">Ops teams</p>
        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Copy-pasting between 5+ tools every day</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-mute leading-relaxed">Your team knows the bottleneck. You just haven't had time to fix it. We scope it in a single call and build it in weeks — not quarters.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-8 lg:p-10">
        <p class="eyebrow text-mute mb-4">Founders</p>
        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Team burning &gt;10 hours/week on manual work</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-mute leading-relaxed">That's a part-time hire you're already paying for in wasted time. We give it back — on a fixed budget, without adding headcount.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-8 lg:p-10">
        <p class="eyebrow text-mute mb-4">Power users</p>
        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Outgrown Zapier or your DIY Airtable setup</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-mute leading-relaxed">You know the tools. You just don't have time to build the right system from scratch. We pick up where your DIY left off.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  USE CASES (dark)                          -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="templates" class="bg-ink text-white dot-grid">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow text-dim mb-4">What it looks like in practice</p>
      <h2 class="h2-display font-bold tracking-tight3 leading-95">Real workflows we've built — adapt one or bring your own.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 -mx-6 lg:mx-0 px-6 lg:px-0 overflow-x-auto h-snap no-scrollbar">
      <div class="flex lg:grid lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5 min-w-max lg:min-w-0">

        <article class="w-[78vw] sm:w-[60vw] lg:w-auto border border-lineDk rounded-md p-7 bg-ink">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">HUBSPOT</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">CLEARBIT</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">SLACK</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-[20px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Lead enrichment &amp; routing</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-dim leading-relaxed">Every new lead is auto-enriched with company data, scored, and routed to the right rep in Slack. No more "who's taking this?"</p>
          <p class="mt-8 font-mono text-[11px] text-accent">Leads routed in &lt;60 seconds</p>
        </article>

        <article class="w-[78vw] sm:w-[60vw] lg:w-auto border border-lineDk rounded-md p-7 bg-ink">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">AIRTABLE</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">STRIPE</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">POSTGRES</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-[20px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Operations dashboard in Airtable</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-dim leading-relaxed">Live revenue, pipeline, and ops metrics in one Airtable view — synced from your billing system, CRM, and product database.</p>
          <p class="mt-8 font-mono text-[11px] text-accent">Revenue + pipeline: one view, always live</p>
        </article>

        <article class="w-[78vw] sm:w-[60vw] lg:w-auto border border-lineDk rounded-md p-7 bg-ink">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">N8N</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">OPENAI</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">GMAIL</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-[20px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">AI-drafted client updates</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-dim leading-relaxed">Project status pulled from your PM tool, summarized by an LLM, drafted as a client-ready email — sent every Friday with one click.</p>
          <p class="mt-8 font-mono text-[11px] text-accent">Friday updates drafted in 30 seconds, not 3 hours</p>
        </article>

        <article class="w-[78vw] sm:w-[60vw] lg:w-auto border border-lineDk rounded-md p-7 bg-ink">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">SHOPIFY</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">AIRTABLE</span>
            <span class="px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-wider rounded border border-lineDk text-dim">QUICKBOOKS</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-[20px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Inventory sync across channels</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-dim leading-relaxed">Stock, orders, and accounting kept in sync across three systems — no nightly CSV exports, no manual reconciliations.</p>
          <p class="mt-8 font-mono text-[11px] text-accent">Reconciliation: 4 hours/month → 0</p>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Client pull-quote placeholder -->
    <div class="mt-14 reveal border border-lineDk rounded-md p-8 lg:p-10 max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-[18px] lg:text-[20px] font-medium leading-relaxed text-white">
        "[CLIENT QUOTE — to be filled in: one sentence on the time or money saved.]"
      </p>
      <p class="mt-5 font-mono text-[11px] text-dim">— [Name], [Role] · [Company]</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 reveal">
      <a href="#book" class="link-u text-[14px] text-dim hover:text-white">See how we'd build yours →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  PROCESS                                   -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="process" class="bg-paper">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-24">

    <p class="font-mono text-[12px] text-dim tracking-wide reveal">50+ workflows shipped · ~22 hrs saved/week · &lt;4 wks first delivery</p>

    <div class="mt-8 max-w-3xl reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow text-mute mb-4">How we work</p>
      <h2 class="h2-display font-bold tracking-tight3 leading-95">From first call to live system in under 4 weeks.</h2>
    </div>

    <ol class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-px bg-line border border-line reveal">
      <li class="bg-paper p-8">
        <div class="font-mono text-[24px] font-bold text-ink">01</div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Discovery call (Week 0)</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-mute leading-relaxed">30 minutes. We map your current tools, the bottlenecks, and what "done" looks like. You leave with a written scope and fixed price.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="bg-paper p-8">
        <div class="font-mono text-[24px] font-bold text-ink">02</div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Build (Weeks 1–3)</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-mute leading-relaxed">We build the system on Airtable + n8n + your existing stack. You see weekly demo videos; nothing is built in a vacuum.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="bg-paper p-8">
        <div class="font-mono text-[24px] font-bold text-ink">03</div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Launch (Week 4)</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-mute leading-relaxed">We deploy live, train your team, and ship documentation written for humans, not engineers.</p>
      </li>
      <li class="bg-paper p-8">
        <div class="font-mono text-[24px] font-bold text-ink">04</div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Maintain (Ongoing)</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-mute leading-relaxed">Optional retainer for changes, monitoring, and the next system. Most clients stay.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  MID-PAGE CTA STRIP                        -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="bg-paper border-t border-b border-line">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-6 reveal">
    <p class="text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2 max-w-lg">
      Most teams already know which workflow they'd automate first. Tell us yours.
    </p>
    <a href="#book" class="cta inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent text-ink text-[14px] font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-md whitespace-nowrap">
      Book a call <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  FAQ                                       -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="faq" class="bg-paper border-t border-line">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow text-mute mb-4">Common questions</p>
      <h2 class="h2-display font-bold tracking-tight3 leading-95">What teams ask before booking.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-line border border-line reveal">
      <div class="bg-paper p-8 lg:p-10">
        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">What does a project typically cost?</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-mute leading-relaxed">Pricing is fixed and scoped after the discovery call. Most projects land between <strong>[FILL IN RANGE]</strong>. No hourly billing, no scope creep, no surprises — you hear the exact number on the call.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-paper p-8 lg:p-10">
        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">What happens if something breaks?</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-mute leading-relaxed">Every system ships with monitoring and error handling — most clients never see a failure surface to users. Retainer clients get same-business-day response on incidents.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-paper p-8 lg:p-10">
        <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold tracking-tight2">Who owns the system after launch?</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] text-mute leading-relaxed">You do. Everything runs in your accounts — your Airtable, your n8n, your databases. We hand over docs written for humans and train your team. The retainer is optional, not a lock-in.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  CLOSING CTA (dark)                        -->
